Default.SignInHeader: Kotahi pūkete mō ngā mea katoa Microsoft
Default.SignInText: Uru ki ō hua me ngā ratonga Microsoft makau mā te pūkete kotahi noa. Ka tūhono tō pūkete Microsoft i a koe ki ngā kōnae, whakaahua, tāngata me ngā ihirangi e kaingākuatia ana e koe i te nui rawa.
Default.L2BackupSubTitle: Tāruatia ōu kōnae, ngā taupānga, ngā manakohanga kia whakaora puta noa i ngā pūrere
Default.L2OtherUserSubTitle: Urunga pūrere, kaiwhakamahi mahi, kura rānei, urunga tautapa wharau hoko
Default.L2FamilySubTitle: Whakahaeretia tō rōpū whānau, whakatikaia ngā momo pūkete, me ngā whakaaetanga pūrere
Default.L2EmailSubTitle: Ngā pūkete e whakamahia e īmēra, e maramataka, e hoapā
Default.L2SignInSubTitle: Windows Hello, kī haumarutanga, kupuhipa, maukati hihiri
Default.L2WorkSchoolSubTitle: Rauemi umanga pērā i te īmēra, te taupānga me te whatunga
Default._L2LinksTitle: Taitara mō te wāhanga rārangi tuemi Hinonga L2
Default.SubscriptionDescription: Ngā taupānga Office mātāmua, te rokiroki kapua OneDrive, me ētahi atu mea
Default.SubscriptionBody: He ohaurunga arotau kotahi hei tiri kia tae kia rima ngā tāngata kei tō whānau. Kei roto ko ngā taupānga huhuatanga mātāmua, tae ki te {{totalMemory}} rokiroki ā-kapua – {{perPersonMemory}} mō ia tangata – me te haumarutanga arā atu anō mō ō pūrere katoa.
Default.ShareHeaderSharing: E tiri ana koe ki a
Default.ShareBody: Ki te rima tāngata rā anō

Default.SubscriptionsSubtitle: Whakahaeretia ngā ratonga me ngā ohaurunga o Microsoft
Default.UpsellDescription: Kotahi ohaurunga mōu hei tiria noatia kia rima atu tāngata. Kei roto hoki ngā taupānga Office mātāmua tae atu kia {{totalBytes}} o te rokiroki kapua ({{bytesPerPerson}} mō ia tangata).
Default.PerpetualsSectionTitle: Ngā hua kua hokona e koe
Default.PerpetualsDescription: Kua tāpirihia ki tō pūkete i te {{date}}
Default.PerpetualsBody: Hei titiro i ngā taipitopito hua, hei tāuta rānei i a Office, haere ki te paemana o tō pūkete Microsoft.
Default.InfoBarMessage: Taro ake nei ka mōnehu tō kāri nama. Me whakahōu ō mōhiohio utunga kia pupuri i tō ohaurunga.
